{"title":"侵越美军雨季谣——调寄浪淘沙","authors":["江南奇"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":7,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"侵越美军雨季谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——调寄浪淘沙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江南奇  诗  吴耘  画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南越雨季已到。西方记者透露：美国侵略军士气更为低落；士兵们躲在防御圈里惴惴不安，生怕外出同解放军作战。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连日雨潺潺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愁绪千端。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"营房藏躲胆犹寒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦里常惊遭袭击，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜夜难安。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最怕出防圈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"性命交关。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去时容易返时难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乒乓一声魂去也，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别了人间。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}